divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving West on I-80 in South Chicago photographing a heavy Chemtrail almost in the direct path of the sun. After reviewing the photos I noticed a cylinder shaped obeject in one of the photos. It appeared to me to be trying to hide in the sunlight. I also noticed a very strange notch in the Chemtrail that it may have produced.
Summary: Cylinder shaped UFO caught between Sun and Chemtrail.
